            "summary": "T9-042 EFCL deterministic controls. Enforced as an executable rule: FC-014 (universal cross-tenant / AI-execution boundary). 45 controls (prefix FC-) carried here for traceability. T9-042 DECIDES; T9-041 GOVERNS AND EXECUTES.",
            "contentText": "PRINCIPLE: T9-042 decides what financial continuity action is appropriate; T9-041 governs and executes it (primaryRuntimeDependency). MODULES: financial-continuity engine, liquidity intelligence, payment-priority framework, bank lien/freeze management, alternate-funding engine, debt & covenant monitoring. 10 financial playbooks: FPB-001 Bank-Lien/Freeze, FPB-002 Bank-Failure, FPB-003 Payment-Network-Outage, FPB-004 Payroll-Continuity, FPB-005 Liquidity-Shortfall, FPB-006 Credit-Facility-Failure, FPB-007 Covenant-Breach, FPB-008 Customer-Fund-Protection, FPB-009 Margin/Collateral-Call, FPB-010 Multi-Bank-Failover. 12 schemas: financial-continuity-event/incident, financial-decision-package, liquidity-position, cash-runway-forecast, payment-obligation, payment-priority-decision, payment-rerouting-proposal, bank-restriction, alternate-funding-source, debt-covenant, customer-fund-protection. 20 events; 45 controls FC-001..FC-045."
